                <dt class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500">Årligt varmeforbrug (kWh)</dt>
                <dd class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-900 sm:col-span-2 sm:mt-0">16.000 kWh varme</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-white px-4 py-5 sm:grid sm:grid-cols-3 sm:gap-4 sm:px-6">
                <dt class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500">Opvarmning (25% gas)</dt>
                <dd class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-900 sm:col-span-2 sm:mt-0">16.000 kWh * 25% => 4.000 kWh varme</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 px-4 py-5 sm:grid sm:grid-cols-3 sm:gap-4 sm:px-6">
                <dt class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500">Opvarmning (75% varmepumpe)</dt>
                <dd class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-900 sm:col-span-2 sm:mt-0">16.000 kWh * 75% => 12.000 kWh varme</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-white px-4 py-5 sm:grid sm:grid-cols-3 sm:gap-4 sm:px-6">
                <dt class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500">Varmeforbrug (gas)</dt>
                <dd class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-900 sm:col-span-2 sm:mt-0">4.000 kWh varme = 400 m3 gas * 25 kr./m3 => 10.000 kr./årligt</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 px-4 py-5 sm:grid sm:grid-cols-3 sm:gap-4 sm:px-6">
                <dt class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500">Varmeforbrug (varmepumpe)</dt>
                <dd class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-900 sm:col-span-2 sm:mt-0">12.000 kWh / 4 SCOP = 3.000 kWh * 3,5 kr./kWh => 10.500 kr./årligt</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-white px-4 py-5 sm:grid sm:grid-cols-3 sm:gap-4 sm:px-6">
                <dt class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500">Samlet varmeforbrug (kr.)</dt>
                <dd class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-900 sm:col-span-2 sm:mt-0">10.000 kr. (gas) + 10.500 kr. (varmepumpe) => 20.500 kr./årligt</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 px-4 py-5 sm:grid sm:grid-cols-3 sm:gap-4 sm:px-6">
                <dt class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500">Abonnement på varmepumpe</dt>
                <dd class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-900 sm:col-span-2 sm:mt-0">410 kr./md. => 4.920 kr./årligt</dd>
